[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Promote improvements to local public transport provision by Buckinghamshire County Council and Transport for Buckinghamshire and local transport service providers and support the activities of all 
[normal]bodies which aim to improve public transport
[normal]1.2
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Independent scrutiny of the policies and priorities of Transport for Buckinghamshire and Rail and Bus companies operating in Aylesbury Vale. 
[normal]1.3
[normal]              
[normal]Act as expert passengers to local public transport service provid
[normal]ers on all 
[normal]              
[normal]relevant aspects of transport provision and transport 
[normal]              
[normal]infrastructure
